_header: I seek a youth that eldeth not
_description: On a religious life — three couplets

BodLauMis210.First Lines:
I seche a þouthe þat eldyth moȝtI seche a lyf
                    þat dyeþ noȝt…
BodLauMis210.Last Lines:
…I seche ful blisse with owte stryfe & þerfore
                    þus I lede my lyf
